Portable Agent Workflow

This repository contains a portable, Markdown-first workflow framework and a
curated skill library for agent-assisted software projects.

The original framework documents, adapters, merge scripts, state templates, and
repository-maintained skills are licensed under the MIT License unless a file or
directory states otherwise.

Some imported or mirrored skills keep their own license and notice files inside
their skill directories. Those local license files continue to govern the
corresponding imported materials.

The Coff0xc/coffee-skill import is tracked in:

- tools/skill-merge/provenance/coffee-skill/

Before redistributing a subset of this repository, preserve the applicable
LICENSE, NOTICE, and provenance files for any included third-party skill.
